NAME memory-augmented-research

# Example using MCP memory server for persistent context
# Requires: mcp.servers.memory configured

INPUT topic
INPUT depth DEFAULT "comprehensive"

AGENT researcher FROM agents/creative-writer.md
AGENT critic FROM agents/devils-advocate.md REQUIRES "reasoning-heavy"

GOAL finalize "Produce final research report from memory. Save the report to research-report-output.md."

CONVERGE iteration "Research $topic thoroughly, storing key findings in memory. Then critically review and refine based on feedback. Output CONVERGED when research is comprehensive and critique yields no major issues." USING researcher, critic WITHIN 3

RUN main USING iteration, finalize
